OL,3,CCouple jailed after pouring boiling
OL,4,Cwater on disabled friend
OL,6,FA couple who poured boiling water on
OL,7,Ftheir disabled friend after an
OL,8,Fargument have been jailed.
OL,10,FThe victim was with Emily Banks and
OL,11,FStephen Turner in on the night of 8
OL,12,FJuly 2023.
OL,14,FThe woman, who is in her 50s, had been
OL,15,Fout for food and drinks with Turner
OL,16,Fbefore Banks joined them at a pub.
OL,18,FAn argument broke out after the three
OL,19,Fof them went to Turner's home in
OL,20,FHazelwood Road - while Turner was
OL,21,Fmaking the victim a cup of coffee.
