OL,3,CCouple jailed after pouring boiling
OL,4,Cwater on disabled friend
OL,6,FTurner, 69, held the kettle and
OL,7,Fflicked boiling water at the victim
OL,8,Fbefore Banks pushed her to the floor.
OL,10,FBanks, 30, then poured the full kettle
OL,11,Fover the victim, who could not get up
OL,12,Fbecause of her disability.
OL,14,FEmergency services were called after
OL,15,Fthe victim sought help from two
OL,16,Fpassers-by after eventually managing
OL,17,Fto escape the property.
OL,19,FTurner and Banks were arrested in the
OL,20,Fearly hours of the following morning.
