OL,6,FThe victim was left with burns to 15%
OL,7,Fof her body and needed extensive
OL,8,Fhospital treatment following the
OL,9,Fattack.
OL,11,FBanks and Turner denied the offence
OL,12,Fbut a trial found them guilty of
OL,13,Fcommitting grievous bodily harm with
OL,14,Fintent.
OL,16,FThe pair appeared at for sentencing on
OL,17,FFriday (8 March) and were jailed for a
OL,18,Fcombined 18 years.
